Yes, I do. Cookies and Cream ice cream is one of my favorites.

I'm not a big cookie fan, but I do like chocolate ice cream with chocolate chips.
That sounds really good. I'll have to try that sometime. What else do you like to do in your free time?
I like to play video games. I've been playing a lot of league of legends lately.
That's cool. I haven't played that in a long time. What's your favorite champion?
My favorite champion is katarina. She's so much fun to play. Do you play any video games?
I used to play a lot when I was younger, but now I don't have much time.
That's too bad. What do you do for a living, if you don't mind me asking?
I work as a cashier at a grocery store. It pays the bills while I go to school.
That sounds like a good job. What are you going to school for, if I may ask?
I am studying to be a veterinarian. I love animals and want to help them.
That's great. I'm sure you'll be able to help a lot of people with that.
I hope so. Do you have any hobbies that you like to do in your spare time?
I like to play video games, but I'm not very good at them. What about you?
I like playing video games as well. I also like to read books. What is your favorite book?
My favorite book is the harry potter series by j. K. Rowling. Have you ever read it?
No, I haven't read that one. I will have to check it out. What other books do you like?
Harry potter is the only book I've ever read. I'm more of a video game person.
That's cool. I like video games too. I play a lot of call of duty. What's your favorite video game?
I don't really have a favorite. I just play whatever is popular at the time. How about you?
I'm a big fan of assassin's creed. Do you play any other video games?
I like assassins creed as well. I do play other games, but I'm not very good at them.

I used to play a lot of league but I haven't played in a while. I am looking for something new to play.
I've heard good things about fortnite. I've never played it, but it looks fun.
Fortnite does look fun. I will have to give it a try. Do you play any other games?

I think you will like it. Do you have any other hobbies besides playing league of legends?
Not really. I don't have a lot of time for hobbies since I work so much.
What do you do for a living, if you don't mind me asking? Do you like it?
I work as a cashier at a grocery store. I like it, but I wish I had more free time.
I can understand that. It's hard to find time to do what you love when you have a full time job.
Yeah, that's true. I guess I just need to find a way to make time for it.
Do you have any hobbies that you like to do in your free time? I like to read.

I like to spend time with my family. We like to go to the beach a lot.
That sounds nice. I wish I had a beach nearby. I live in the suburbs.
Do you have any pets? I have a dog, a cat, and a parrot.
I do not have pets. I would like to get a dog. What kind of dog do you have?
I have an australian shepherd. I love him so much. Do you like dogs?
I do like dogs. I used to have a golden retriever when I was a kid.
That's cool. I've always wanted a dog but I don't think I have the time to take care of one.
Yeah, they can be a lot of work, but it's worth it in the long run.
I'll have to think about it. Maybe I'll get one when I'm done with school.
Yeah, that's a good idea. I'm sure you'll have plenty of free time once you graduate.
I hope so. It's hard to find time when you have so much homework to do.

I would have to say that my favorite book by her is the catcher in the rye.

I would say it is a good place to start. It is one of my favorite books of all time.

It is just a really good book. It has a lot of twists and turns that keep you on your toes.
That sounds really interesting. I'll have to check it out. What other books do you like?
